      <title>特朗普内阁官员在小组聊天板上面对诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-cabinet-officials-in-group-chat-flap-face-a-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统内阁的五名成员在诉讼中被指控违反了美国法律，该法律旨在通过使用加密的消息传递平台信号来保护政府记录，以沟通有关正式业务的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-cabinet-officials-in-group-chat-flap-face-a-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 00:12:03 GMT</pubDate>
