    <item>
      <title>参议院确认Jay Bhattacharya领导NIH</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/senate-confirms-jay-bhattacharya-to-lead-nih</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院投票决定确认斯坦福大学卫生经济学家和医师Jay Bhattacharya领导美国国立卫生研究院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/senate-confirms-jay-bhattacharya-to-lead-nih</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 22:30:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FHFA首席目的计划旨在帮助首次购房者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/fhfa-chief-ends-program-designed-to-help-first-time-homebuyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦住房金融机构的负责人命令结束房利美和弗雷迪MAC计划，旨在通过提供付款和结束援助来支持首次购房者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/fhfa-chief-ends-program-designed-to-help-first-time-homebuyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 22:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯将英国支出减少了数十亿英镑：值得关注的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/reeves-to-cut-uk-spending-by-billions-of-pounds-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的总理将归咎于全球经济逆风，因为面对自己在自己的工党内部越来越多的批评，她冒着疏远选民的批评，她将英国政府支出削减了数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/reeves-to-cut-uk-spending-by-billions-of-pounds-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党更靠近减税计划，眼睛债务上限协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/republicans-move-closer-to-tax-cut-plan-eye-debt-ceiling-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党领导人说，他们正在就一项计划，以通过唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的2017年减税和增加债务上限的计划达成共识，因为国会希望在5月底批准经济方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/republicans-move-closer-to-tax-cut-plan-eye-debt-ceiling-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 21:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约要求特朗普尽管威胁要收取过境资金，但仍要求更多的MTA援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ny-asks-trump-for-more-mta-aid-amid-threat-to-pull-transit-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约官员呼吁联邦政府向纽约市的公共交通系统提供更多援助，即使特朗普政府加强了其退缩资金的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ny-asks-trump-for-more-mta-aid-amid-threat-to-pull-transit-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 21:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>魁北克认为，随着贸易战的叮咬，赤字更深，增长速度较慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/quebec-sees-deeper-deficit-lower-growth-amid-tariff-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克省是加拿大第二大省，预测下一个财政年度惊人的136亿加元（95亿美元）的赤字，并警告说，预算前景取决于与美国贸易战争的持续时间和严重性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/quebec-sees-deeper-deficit-lower-growth-amid-tariff-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的哥伦比亚资金停止提起学术联盟诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-columbia-funding-halt-draws-suit-from-academic-unions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个教育工会起诉特朗普政府从哥伦比亚大学收到4亿美元的联邦资金，称此举是为了限制校园内的学术独立和言论自由的非法企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-columbia-funding-halt-draws-suit-from-academic-unions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持华尔兹，审查聊天后的信号应用程序使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他的政府正在调查一名新闻记者向也门的一组高级官员，讨论军事罢工计划，但表示支持国家安全顾问迈克尔·沃尔兹（Michael Waltz）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚宣布减税，预算支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚左翼政府在选举前的预算中揭示了减税和其他甜味剂，旨在缓解选民的生活成本，并帮助赢得总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）的第二任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
